56:39.083 --> 56:40.351
Look.

56:55.065 --> 56:57.002
What has he done
to you this time?

57:12.583 --> 57:15.619
We call this... a "boat."

57:21.257 --> 57:22.627
You see?

57:40.444 --> 57:41.612
What?

58:51.482 --> 58:53.217
I found a rowboat.

58:54.618 --> 58:56.617
I know of it.

58:56.619 --> 59:00.322
Sorry, what?
Why didn't you say so?

59:00.324 --> 59:02.123
Wouldn't do you no good.

59:02.125 --> 59:03.625
